gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 130, Spurs 118
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Spurs, 130-118. Lauri Markkanen led the way for the Jazz with 31 points, 12 rebounds and five 3PM, while Jordan Clarkson added 24 points, six rebounds and eight assists in the victory. Keldon Johnson tallied a team-high 26 points for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Jazz have won three consecutive games as they improve to 13-18 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 4-25.
